00:08:12.189 --> 00:08:15.400 line:93%
The angel's wings I saw at Soo Chang's old orphanage.

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:17.770 line:93%
Then Lee Doo Sik and Jin Soo A.

00:08:18.900 --> 00:08:21.100 line:93%
Everything is connected to that orphanage.

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:27.580 line:93%
Why did she do this?

00:08:34.180 --> 00:08:35.249 line:93%
Why?

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.300 line:93%
Why are you sitting here like this?

