She had the tattoo too.

00:09:00.139 --> 00:09:02.840 line:93%
It was the little girl Doo Sik had a crush on.

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:03.980 line:93%
It's Jin Soo A, isn't it?

00:09:07.820 --> 00:09:09.320 line:93%
What brings you here again?

00:09:10.350 --> 00:09:12.989 line:93%
The person who comes here to see the angel's wings...

00:09:13.190 --> 00:09:16.619 line:93%
The same person who has a tattoo of that on her neck...

00:09:18.730 --> 00:09:21.859 line:93%
killed two people to this point and is willing to kill more.

00:09:25.499 --> 00:09:26.769 line:93%
Jin Soo A.

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:31.539 line:93%
- Why would she... - Where is she right now?

00:09:31.539 --> 00:09:32.909 line:93%
Soo A...

00:09:35.210 --> 00:09:37.749 line:93%
I have no idea.

00:09:38.649 --> 00:09:41.680 line:93%
She's lying. She was just here.

00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:44.420 line:93%
I know that she was just here.

00:09:44.420 --> 00:09:46.989 line:93%
Someone saw her, and I checked her credit card transaction.

00:09:46.989 --> 00:09:50.220 line:93%
There's really no telling in where she'll be.

00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:53.129 line:93%
- Where is she? - I don't know.

00:09:58.230 --> 00:10:00.300 line:93%
I need a lead, ma'am.

00:10:05.369 --> 00:10:07.409 line:93%
What kind of a person is she?

00:10:08.310 --> 00:10:09.580 line:93%
She lost...

00:10:11.210 --> 00:10:13.450 line:93%
both of her parents at once,

00:10:13.879 --> 00:10:15.519 line:93%
then shut off her mouth and ears...

00:10:15.519 --> 00:10:17.720 line:93%
because of that shock.

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:19.850 line:93%
She's a very weak person.

00:10:19.850 --> 00:10:22.289 line:93%
