00:10:22.289 --> 00:10:23.460 line:93%
But still,

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:25.659 line:93%
if you gave her a little bit of love,

00:10:25.659 --> 00:10:28.330 line:93%
she would blindly return it back to you.

00:10:28.499 --> 00:10:30.259 line:93%
Yes, she was pretty odd.

00:10:30.529 --> 00:10:32.470 line:93%
She was there, but it felt like she never was.

00:10:33.970 --> 00:10:36.539 line:93%
Director Tak Jung Hwan's special donation.

00:10:38.039 --> 00:10:40.840 line:93%
Was she the one who received that donation?

00:10:42.009 --> 00:10:43.609 line:93%
How did you know...

