00:11:19.450 --> 00:11:20.879 line:93%
And Tak Jae Hee.

00:11:23.019 --> 00:11:25.149 line:93%
He didn't seem to know anything.

00:11:25.389 --> 00:11:27.460 line:93%
I don't know what's going on,

00:11:27.560 --> 00:11:30.190 line:93%
but she's the person who attacked Gong Soo Chang.

