00:11:36.300 --> 00:11:40.369 line:93%
for one reason or another, Tak Jung Hwan tried to cover it up.

00:11:40.730 --> 00:11:44.239 line:93%
If Director Tak trained Jin Soo A...

00:11:45.539 --> 00:11:48.980 line:93%
