00:11:48.980 --> 00:11:50.440 line:93%
I don't get it.

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:52.409 line:93%
What about me?

00:11:52.850 --> 00:11:53.950 line:93%
Why me?

00:11:54.619 --> 00:11:55.950 line:93%
Her parents...

00:11:57.350 --> 00:12:00.019 line:93%
were the couple who died in the Incheon five-way car crash.

00:12:03.359 --> 00:12:06.129 line:93%
You weren't the only victim of that accident.

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:11.529 line:93%
The couple in the victim's car.

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:18.670 line:93%
They had a family member left behind.

00:12:19.269 --> 00:12:20.840 line:93%
Like you, Soo Chang.

00:12:23.409 --> 00:12:25.480 line:93%
