00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:54.839 line:93%
Select your locker.

00:19:11.890 --> 00:19:12.890 line:93%
Mr. Oh.

00:19:13.349 --> 00:19:14.519 line:93%
When you come over,

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:18.029 line:93%
please bring the photographs from the Incheon junction...

00:19:18.489 --> 00:19:20.059 line:93%
traffic accident from 16 years ago.

00:19:23.029 --> 00:19:24.059 line:93%
Thank you.

00:19:29.569 --> 00:19:30.599 line:93%
Hello.

00:19:31.269 --> 00:19:33.440 line:93%
- I'm hungry. - Come in.

00:19:38.009 --> 00:19:40.180 line:93%
I thought I would die. I feel better now.

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:41.779 line:93%
Why didn't you eat dinner?

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:43.819 line:93%
I wanted to ask your dad...

00:19:43.819 --> 00:19:46.489 line:93%
some questions over dinner, but he isn't in.

00:19:46.489 --> 00:19:47.819 line:93%
- My father? - Yes.

00:19:48.819 --> 00:19:50.420 line:93%
You know my dad's case, right?

00:19:50.420 --> 00:19:53.160 line:93%
Of course. It's the reason you became a reporter.

00:19:53.390 --> 00:19:55.529 line:93%
I'm looking into it again.

00:19:55.529 --> 00:19:58.670 line:93%
I asked Detective Cha and your dad for help.

00:19:59.230 --> 00:20:01.400 line:93%
The case Detective Cha is on...

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:04.170 line:93%
is connected to my dad's last case.

00:20:04.410 --> 00:20:07.980 line:93%
If he can solve this one, it might help solve my dad's case.

00:20:10.079 --> 00:20:13.110 line:93%
- Really? - Your dad said something odd today.

00:20:13.610 --> 00:20:15.620 line:93%
There's so little evidence left.

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:18.690 line:93%
The witness is dead too.

00:20:19.420 --> 00:20:21.589 line:93%
He said the witness was dead.

00:20:22.120 --> 00:20:23.960 line:93%
But my dad's case...

00:20:24.460 --> 00:20:25.860 line:93%
had no witnesses.

00:20:26.529 --> 00:20:28.299 line:93%
That's what I wanted to ask.

00:20:28.759 --> 00:20:31.970 line:93%
He must be busy because he's about to become a minister.

00:20:32.170 --> 00:20:34.140 line:93%
Yes, I guess so.

00:20:35.970 --> 00:20:37.710 line:93%
He went from cop to prosecutor...

00:20:37.839 --> 00:20:40.779 line:93%
and now to Minister of Justice. He's incredible.

00:20:42.279 --> 00:20:44.249 line:93%
What do you think of him?

00:20:45.079 --> 00:20:47.380 line:93%
- What? - Not the boring stuff...

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:48.749 line:93%
you get online.

00:20:48.950 --> 00:20:51.390 line:93%
What do you think he's like?

00:20:54.589 --> 00:20:56.390 line:93%
- I don't know. - What?

00:20:57.529 --> 00:20:58.660 line:93%
What about you?

00:20:59.589 --> 00:21:01.559 line:93%
- What? - What are you like?

00:21:04.829 --> 00:21:05.970 line:93%
Jin Soo A.

00:21:06.170 --> 00:21:08.200 line:93%
She committed murder twice already.

00:21:09.769 --> 00:21:13.610 line:93%
If she followed Tak Jung Hwan so blindly, why...

00:21:13.610 --> 00:21:15.809 line:93%
- Detective Cha. - Anyway,

00:21:16.009 --> 00:21:19.509 line:93%
if we get Jin Soo A's testimony that she's been forced to commit murder,

00:21:20.380 --> 00:21:21.779 line:93%
we'll be able to get the director.

00:21:21.779 --> 00:21:23.450 line:93%
I think, Detective Cha,

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:25.650 line:93%
something strange is happening to me.

00:21:26.620 --> 00:21:27.690 line:93%
What?

00:21:29.460 --> 00:21:30.620 line:93%
I think...

00:21:31.989 --> 00:21:33.890 line:93%
my body is disappearing.

00:21:35.630 --> 00:21:36.700 line:93%
What?

00:21:42.039 --> 00:21:44.440 line:93%
Gosh, it's better now.

00:21:44.440 --> 00:21:45.640 line:93%
Why is it like that?

00:21:46.039 --> 00:21:47.410 line:93%
I don't know.

00:21:47.940 --> 00:21:50.640 line:93%
But it's worse than last time.

00:21:50.640 --> 00:21:53.110 line:93%
Wait. It's not the first time? When did it start happening?

00:21:53.110 --> 00:21:54.220 line:93%
It started...

00:21:54.650 --> 00:21:56.420 line:93%
when we were at the police station.

00:21:56.980 --> 00:21:58.690 line:93%
Is he always jealous or what?

00:22:00.120 --> 00:22:02.519 line:93%
And then, it happened at the orphanage.

00:22:04.160 --> 00:22:05.230 line:93%
I...

00:22:06.259 --> 00:22:08.099 line:93%
What's wrong with me?

00:22:08.460 --> 00:22:09.499 line:93%
Wait.

00:22:10.529 --> 00:22:12.200 line:93%
I... I'm not seeing things, right?

00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:15.200 line:93%
I saw my hand disappear too.

00:22:15.200 --> 00:22:17.239 line:93%
What should we do? Why is this happening?

00:22:17.239 --> 00:22:19.170 line:93%
I don't know. I don't...

00:22:19.710 --> 00:22:22.710 line:93%
Right. Miss Bong might know.

00:22:27.880 --> 00:22:29.980 line:93%
Disappearance.

00:22:29.980 --> 00:22:31.089 line:93%
What?

00:22:32.489 --> 00:22:34.390 line:93%
Is he going to disappear forever?

00:22:34.390 --> 00:22:36.259 line:93%
So I'm not just going to die?

00:22:36.259 --> 00:22:37.960 line:93%
I'm going to disappear like smoke?

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:41.259 line:93%
In a few days, the 49 days you had will be over.

00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:42.630 line:93%
You don't have much time.

00:22:45.269 --> 00:22:46.730 line:93%
Do something.

00:22:46.730 --> 00:22:48.339 line:93%
You trust me, right?

00:22:49.140 --> 00:22:50.640 line:93%
Then trust me until the end.

00:22:52.210 --> 00:22:54.440 line:93%
But there...

00:22:58.749 --> 00:22:59.809 line:93%
Hey.

00:23:00.349 --> 00:23:01.680 line:93%
Later...

00:23:03.450 --> 00:23:06.019 line:93%
A little later, something will happen that will make you cry.

00:23:06.019 --> 00:23:08.259 line:93%
But don't blame yourself.

00:23:08.920 --> 00:23:11.489 line:93%
That's what destiny is like.

00:23:11.489 --> 00:23:13.289 line:93%
It's always so mean.

00:23:13.890 --> 00:23:14.999 line:93%
It'd have been better...

00:23:15.759 --> 00:23:18.370 line:93%
if you hadn't got to know that person.

00:23:22.140 --> 00:23:27.110 line:93%
(Seoul Central Police Station)

00:23:27.110 --> 00:23:28.640 line:93%
Why are you here?

00:23:29.309 --> 00:23:31.180 line:93%
I came to lend you this.

00:23:34.249 --> 00:23:37.890 line:93%
- I had a rough day. - That's why I'm here.

00:23:39.150 --> 00:23:41.190 line:93%
By the way, I met Jae Hee.

00:23:41.190 --> 00:23:43.519 line:93%
I went to see Jung Hwan, but he wasn't in.

00:23:43.920 --> 00:23:46.289 line:93%
He had told me something strange.

00:23:46.289 --> 00:23:48.700 line:93%
He said that the witness to my dad's accident had died.

00:23:48.700 --> 00:23:51.200 line:93%
But there was no witness to my dad's accident.

00:23:53.670 --> 00:23:56.539 line:93%
He told you that the witness had died?

00:23:56.870 --> 00:23:57.970 line:93%
Yes.

00:24:01.680 --> 00:24:02.809 line:93%
Why?

00:24:05.880 --> 00:24:07.279 line:93%
It's nothing.

00:24:09.349 --> 00:24:12.450 line:93%
How's Soo Chang?

00:24:13.819 --> 00:24:15.420 line:93%
Keep this a secret to Ssong.

00:24:15.789 --> 00:24:19.089 line:93%
She... She might get upset.

00:24:19.559 --> 00:24:20.930 line:93%
He's doing fine.

00:24:21.430 --> 00:24:22.700 line:93%
It's good to hear that.

00:24:25.569 --> 00:24:27.069 line:93%
"Chocolate cream bread".

00:24:27.370 --> 00:24:30.099 line:93%
"Make chocolate cream and a dough."

00:24:30.099 --> 00:24:32.210 line:93%
"Strong flour, sugar, dry..."

00:24:32.239 --> 00:24:34.809 line:93%
Strong flour might be too much.

00:24:34.809 --> 00:24:37.380 line:93%
"Shape the dough, and bake it on a saucepan."

00:24:37.380 --> 00:24:41.120 line:93%
"Then you'll have made some wavy chocolate cream."

00:24:41.120 --> 00:24:42.980 line:93%
This is what you like best.

00:24:44.089 --> 00:24:45.720 line:93%
Ko Bong.

00:24:47.660 --> 00:24:49.960 line:93%
Do you think I'll be able to catch the culprit?

00:24:54.630 --> 00:24:56.999 line:93%
Will I be able to go back into my body?

00:24:59.230 --> 00:25:00.430 line:93%
It's easy.

00:25:01.499 --> 00:25:03.069 line:93%
I'll make it for you.

00:25:03.870 --> 00:25:06.769 line:93%
"Corn bread. Prepare a meat slice,"

00:25:06.769 --> 00:25:10.950 line:93%
"and put ham, corn, onion, and green pepper."

00:25:12.410 --> 00:25:15.349 line:93%
This time, I got wet.

00:25:15.920 --> 00:25:18.190 line:93%
What would I do with my wet clothes?

00:25:18.890 --> 00:25:20.150 line:93%
You have...

00:25:20.819 --> 00:25:22.089 line:93%
to protect her.

00:25:25.489 --> 00:25:27.930 line:93%
"October 25, 2001".

00:25:28.160 --> 00:25:30.999 line:93%
"We promised to meet at night."

00:25:30.999 --> 00:25:34.569 line:93%
"But he called me at 8pm, saying he's going to be late."

00:25:39.210 --> 00:25:41.180 line:93%
Before he called me,

00:25:42.110 --> 00:25:44.309 line:93%
he could have called someone.

00:25:47.309 --> 00:25:49.980 line:93%
Why didn't I think of this before?

00:25:49.980 --> 00:25:52.220 line:93%
If I find the person he had been talking to at that time,

00:25:52.589 --> 00:25:55.789 line:93%
there's a high possibility that person might know something.

00:25:57.120 --> 00:25:59.460 line:93%
I'll need to find that person first.

00:26:10.870 --> 00:26:12.470 line:93%
(Song Ji Seok, the detective in charge of the Incheon car accident)

00:26:12.470 --> 00:26:14.110 line:93%
(Kim Jong Doo, someone forced him to bear false testimony)

00:26:14.110 --> 00:26:15.480 line:93%
(Jo Hang Joon, died while investigating Kim Jong Doo's case)

00:26:15.480 --> 00:26:17.279 line:93%
(Tak Jung Hwan, Jin Soo A)

00:26:18.249 --> 00:26:19.610 line:93%
I'll get him.

00:26:21.249 --> 00:26:23.150 line:93%
Just hang in there, Soo Chang.

00:26:28.989 --> 00:26:30.690 line:93%
- You should have some coffee. - Thanks.

00:26:37.329 --> 00:26:38.430 line:93%
I need to listen again.

00:26:44.470 --> 00:26:46.910 line:93%
(Intensive Care Unit)

00:26:46.910 --> 00:26:48.039 line:93%
Hello.

00:27:17.610 --> 00:27:19.809 line:93%
(Seoul Central Police Station)

00:27:22.640 --> 00:27:23.640 line:93%
Hello.

00:27:26.309 --> 00:27:28.220 line:93%
- Are you all right? - I'm fine.

00:27:28.220 --> 00:27:29.749 line:93%
I'm not dead yet.

00:27:31.390 --> 00:27:34.049 line:93%
I'm strong-willed, you know?

00:27:38.259 --> 00:27:39.430 line:93%
(Distinct Features: angel wing tattoo on the neck)

00:27:39.430 --> 00:27:40.690 line:93%
(Moved from Japan to Korea in 2016)

00:27:40.690 --> 00:27:42.160 line:93%
(From Haneul Orphanage, was supported by Director Tak)

00:27:42.259 --> 00:27:44.269 line:93%
(Tracking Situation of the Suspect, Jin Soo A)

00:27:44.670 --> 00:27:49.069 line:93%
Gosh, we were on stakeout all night, but we got nothing.

00:27:49.069 --> 00:27:52.670 line:93%
I know. Maybe we lost her.

00:27:53.440 --> 00:27:56.440 line:93%
Where's Dokgo? Why isn't he here?

00:27:57.279 --> 00:27:58.309 line:93%
This lighter.

00:27:59.809 --> 00:28:02.450 line:93%
- What? - It wasn't just any lighter.

00:28:12.230 --> 00:28:13.589 line:93%
Please concentrate.

00:28:14.599 --> 00:28:17.730 line:93%
It starts now.

00:28:27.239 --> 00:28:30.880 line:93%
I thought you had been compensated enough.

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:34.420 line:93%
I spent all that money. I have none left anymore.

00:28:36.650 --> 00:28:38.049 line:93%
So you want more?

00:28:38.249 --> 00:28:40.349 line:93%
The statute of limitations has expired.

00:28:40.349 --> 00:28:42.720 line:93%
If I say...

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:44.489 line:93%
Won't they investigate again?

00:28:48.130 --> 00:28:51.769 line:93%
If I give you the money, you won't tell...

00:28:52.069 --> 00:28:53.230 line:93%
Killing...

00:28:54.470 --> 00:28:55.569 line:93%
I see.

00:28:56.269 --> 00:28:59.170 line:93%
- I'll call you in three days. - I'll be waiting.

00:28:59.239 --> 00:29:02.980 line:93%
I'll be waiting at... In three days.

00:29:03.779 --> 00:29:06.980 line:93%
Hey. What's all this about?

00:29:06.980 --> 00:29:09.880 line:93%
So someone committed murder, right?

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:10.989 line:93%
No way.

00:29:11.249 --> 00:29:15.120 line:93%
It was a recorder that looked like a lighter.

00:29:15.390 --> 00:29:17.989 line:93%
There's a bit of static,

00:29:17.989 --> 00:29:19.529 line:93%
but I'll find out...

00:29:19.529 --> 00:29:22.700 line:93%
who was on that recorder in no time...

00:29:22.700 --> 00:29:23.730 line:93%
by analyzing the components.

00:29:23.730 --> 00:29:26.970 line:93%
You don't need to. It's Director Tak.

00:29:32.210 --> 00:29:34.739 line:93%
It's me. How have you been?

00:29:34.940 --> 00:29:39.079 line:93%
There's been a burglary at my house a few days ago.

00:29:39.549 --> 00:29:42.420 line:93%
The burglar went through everything, but nothing went missing.

00:29:42.420 --> 00:29:44.989 line:93%
- So I didn't report to the police. - A burglar?

00:29:45.190 --> 00:29:47.819 line:93%
But there was something weird.

00:29:48.989 --> 00:29:50.519 line:93%
Hang Joon's urn?

00:29:50.519 --> 00:29:52.690 line:93%
The janitor called and said...

00:29:52.690 --> 00:29:55.460 line:93%
someone had searched through it.

00:29:55.460 --> 00:29:57.529 line:93%
He warned me not to put any valuables in there.

00:29:58.029 --> 00:29:59.029 line:93%
When did this happen?

00:29:59.029 --> 00:30:02.400 line:93%
Here it is. December 5, 2017.

00:30:02.400 --> 00:30:04.410 line:93%
This is where his urn is, right?

00:30:04.509 --> 00:30:06.940 line:93%
Dongducheon gas station. She refueled here.

00:30:06.940 --> 00:30:07.980 line:93%
All right.

00:30:07.980 --> 00:30:10.239 line:93%
Thank you. I'll go visit Jun Soo soon.

00:30:11.309 --> 00:30:12.549 line:93%
Jin Soo A...

00:30:13.950 --> 00:30:15.980 line:93%
must have been looking for this.

00:30:18.890 --> 00:30:22.890 line:93%
This is why Director Tak had to kill Hang Joon.

00:30:23.259 --> 00:30:24.460 line:93%
His secret...

00:30:25.360 --> 00:30:27.700 line:93%
was hidden inside this lighter.

00:30:28.759 --> 00:30:29.900 line:93%
Right.

00:30:30.460 --> 00:30:32.269 line:93%
This is what Detective Jo found...

00:30:32.269 --> 00:30:34.029 line:93%
at the place of Kim Jong Doo's incident.

00:30:34.069 --> 00:30:37.140 line:93%
That's also why she ransacked the police station,

00:30:37.339 --> 00:30:39.769 line:93%
his house, and his urn.

00:30:39.769 --> 00:30:43.239 line:93%
If Kim Jong Doo had simply been a witness to a car accident,

00:30:44.180 --> 00:30:47.779 line:93%
Director Tak wouldn't have had to silence him.

00:30:47.950 --> 00:30:50.319 line:93%
The statute of limitations for the destruction of evidence...

00:30:50.319 --> 00:30:52.519 line:93%
of the car accident 16 years ago has already been expired.

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:56.289 line:93%
It was too weak to be a reason for him to want to kill him.

00:30:57.220 --> 00:30:59.390 line:93%
But if this is about murder, it's a different story.

00:31:08.839 --> 00:31:10.039 line:93%
I haven't...

00:31:10.739 --> 00:31:13.110 line:93%
- quit smoking yet. - Kim Jong Doo...

00:31:13.110 --> 00:31:14.739 line:93%
went to Director Tak...

00:31:14.739 --> 00:31:17.110 line:93%
right after returning back to Korea.

00:31:17.480 --> 00:31:20.210 line:93%
He knew Director Tak would do a body search on him,

00:31:20.210 --> 00:31:21.819 line:93%
and of course, he'd take away his phone too.

00:31:22.849 --> 00:31:24.890 line:93%
He probably had to come up with an idea.

00:31:29.620 --> 00:31:31.460 line:93%
And he probably threatened him...

00:31:32.690 --> 00:31:34.430 line:93%
with that voice recording.

00:31:34.559 --> 00:31:36.499 line:93%
You can't be like this.

00:31:36.799 --> 00:31:38.670 line:93%
I have a voice recording of you.

00:31:38.670 --> 00:31:40.700 line:93%
Come on, Director Tak. This is very unlike you.

00:31:40.700 --> 00:31:42.940 line:93%
How much do you want?

00:31:43.470 --> 00:31:45.640 line:93%
But there's something that Kim didn't know.

00:31:46.339 --> 00:31:49.380 line:93%
Director Tak had something which he didn't have...

00:31:49.739 --> 00:31:51.049 line:93%
16 years ago.

00:31:51.950 --> 00:31:53.210 line:93%
Jin Soo A.

00:31:55.234 --> 00:31:56.834 line:93%
(Episode 30 will air shortly.)

